text: Ðis synd þes landes gemæro æt lecham stede.
Ærest on dene pit of þam pytte on þone hnottan þorn.
Of þam þorne on wines treow.
Of wines treowe on ðan readan hane.
Of stigeal hammum on wigferðes leage norþe wearde.
Þanon þreores ofer wræstles hylle on buccan crundel.
Of buccan crundele on þa haran apeldere þanon andlang standene.
Oð gyddan dene þweores ofer weardan dune.
Oð þa dene andlang þære dene eft on dene pit.
